_sText:
This map was made for the "Dangerous Cargo" Mapping contest on GameBanana


Background:

Terrorist have hijacked a goverment cargo truck loaded with highley explosive materials. On their route to their destination, the hijackers crashed the vehicle into a wall making the vehicle unusuable. Without hesitation, the Terrorists have taken shelter within a warehouse and have taken hostages. Time is running out, and one side must make it's call!
